<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><br/></div><en-media hash="4d943f93b50f3185fb688ba4865249ac" type="image/png" style="--en-naturalWidth:1562; --en-naturalHeight:470;" /><div>recording of call:</div><div style="--en-richlink:true; --en-href:https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NVTFtF9UnINJdPmbfINJ0p_QyY2Ps8ff/view?usp=sharing; --en-title:optimize 365.mp4; --en-viewAs:minimal;"><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NVTFtF9UnINJdPmbfINJ0p_QyY2Ps8ff/view?usp=sharing" rev="en_rl_small">optimize 365.mp4</a></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>Shimon CTO, CS, Ofek air force</div><div>CICD company sold to harness</div><div>founded claudia - in the US legal tech</div><div>preseed from entree - 2 years later realized cost of acquisition was high , crouded market, left</div><div>august 2024 met Shay and decided to do cyber for MSPS</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>Shai - writes code from 13 - was sportay in the army - american footbal, did linux course, tinkal secure voip - devops engineer to vp engineer and security</div><div>worked in Thailand - with big providers millions of user</div><div><br/></div><div>interviewed 100 msps and mssps - </div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>AI security agent - objective to know all the security solutions, help setup the configuration, now expanding to integrations with sentinalone </div><div><br/></div><div>product is for MSSP and MSP</div><div>first - assessment of the security, configure setup etc</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>Cyderis</div><div>NTT data poc</div><div><br/></div><div>sell per user and not per tenant</div><div><br/></div><en-media hash="d65975bb8e115514dd9ad1c23b211d34" type="image/png" style="--en-naturalWidth:1680; --en-naturalHeight:982;" /><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>sspm solution providers   are a solution for big companies but not for MSPS</div><div><br/></div><div>usability varies - from every day to weekly to monthly</div><div><br/></div><div>Pros:</div><div>Valuable</div><div>Powerful</div><div>opportunity for bigger revenue from a cut of the recommended new packages</div><div><br/></div><div>Cons:</div><div>Shay is a hustler for good and bad</div><div>check the usability per msp </div><div><br/></div><div>bottom line:</div><div>interesting, pending deeper product and tech understanding, ref call with an ssp and usage pattern review, would be also great to connect to the angels that invested and understand their reasoning</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>who will buy this? -  Guards, Cynomy acronys</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div></en-note>      